---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Payroll Services"
  description="Tax Doctor offers a comprehensive payroll service including salary processing, payslips, EMP201, EMP501 and IRP5 submissions."
  keywords="payroll, paye, emp201, emp501, irp5, uif, sdl, payslips, johannesburg"
>
  <div class="section">
    <h2>Payroll</h2>
    <img class="image-section" alt="Payroll" src="/images/Services/taxpayroll.jpg" />
    <p>We offer a comprehensive payroll service which includes:</p>
    <ul class="alt">
      <li>Recording of employee details</li>
      <li>Payment of salaries</li>
      <li>Generation of payslips</li>
      <li>Submission to SARS of EMP201 incl. UIF and SDL</li>
      <li>Submission to SARS of Annual/Bi-Annual EMP501 reconciliations</li>
      <li>Provision of IRP5/IT3(a) for each employee</li>
      <li>Customised reports e.g. summary reports of employees' income, deductions and net amounts to be paid</li>
    </ul>
    <p>All this is electronically captured into the relevant accounting software.</p>
  </div>
</Layout>
